quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,"Ndahiye imiyaga ihuha cyane igatatanya (ibicu, ikazamura ivumbi, umusenyi n’ibindi)"
  51,2,N’ibyikoreye imitwaro (ibicu biremereye bitwara imvura)
  51,3,N’ibigenda mu buryo bworoshye (amato agenda mu nyanja)
  51,4,N’abashinzwe gukwirakwiza igeno (abamalayika)
  51,5,Mu by’ukuri ibyo musezeranywa (izuka n’ibindi bizaba ku munsi w’imperuka) ni impamo
  51,6,"Kandi rwose, kuzagororerwa (cyangwa guhanwa ku bakoze ibibi) bizabaho nta kabuza"
  51,7,Ndahiye ikirere kirimo amayira gikoze neza
  51,8,Rwose mufite imvugo zitandukanye (ku byerekeye intumwa Muhamadi ndetse n’iyi Qur’an)
  51,9,Uteshwa (gukurikira Qur’an n’intumwa Muhamadi) ni uwateshejwe (gukurikira ukuri)
  51,10,Abanyabinyoma baravumwe
  51,11,"Ba bandi bari mu bujiji, barangaye"
  51,12,Barabaza igihe umunsi w’ibihembo uzabera
  51,13,(Uzaba ari) umunsi bazaba bari mu muriro bahanwa
  51,14,(Bazabwirwa bati) “Ngaho nimwumve ibihano byanyu; ibi ni byo mwajyaga musaba ko byihutishwa.”
  51,15,Mu by’ukuri abagandukira Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’amariba (yo mu Ijuru)
  51,16,Bakira ibyo Nyagasani wabo yabahaye. Mu by’ukuri mbere bari abakora ibyiza
  51,17,"Bajyaga baryama gake mu ijoro (kubera ko babaga basali, basingiza Nyagasani wabo)"
  51,18,No mu gicuku (mu rukerera babaga) basaba imbabazi (Allah)
  51,19,"No mu mitungo yabo, habagamo umugabane bagenera abakene basaba n’abihishira"
  51,20,No ku isi hari ibimenyetso ku bemera badashidikanya
  51,21,Ndetse no muri mwe ubwanyu (ibyo bimenyetso birimo). Ese ntimubona
  51,22,No mu kirere hari amafunguro yanyu ndetse n’ibyo musezeranywa
  51,23,"Bityo, ndahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani w’ikirere n’isi ko (ibyo musezeranywa) ari ukuri nko kuvuga kwanyu"